data.description: Enjoy Bitterroot Valley views from every direction from this 3.29 acre property in Stevensville. This property features two homes, a detached garage, and a shed. The first home has single level living, with three bedrooms and one full bathroom. Walk in to a cozy and large living room with a wood burning stove and fireplace. Off of the living area are three good sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. A light filled dining area and located just off the kitchen with mountain views. Downstairs is an unfinished basement with a partially complete half bathroom and a blank canvas for you to finish. The guest house has one bedroom and one bathroom and has been a quality long term rental for the seller for years. Outbuildings include a detached two car garage and a shed for storage. Call Danni Moore, 406-396-2442, or your real estate professional to schedule a private showing.
